<plot>In this format, with some variations over the many seasons, a presenter in the studio announces, wraps or reads text and/or footage about various 'boulevard' news in Flanders, such as new film and TV releases, theatrical shows, the life of Flemish and foreign celebrities, beauty contests, media events... usually there's a few weekly or annual items, sometimes with a specific second presenter, such as Ward Verrijcken who reports on Hollywood, film festivals etc., 'festival Bob' on musical (summer) festivals.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?132245</url></doc>
